response.text:
Here’s a TekAutomate Steps UI flow for your MSO4/5/6 Series scope, using only real step types and verified SCPI commands. This configures CH1/CH2, sets up I2C decode, adds setup/hold time measurements, sets the trigger, performs a single acquisition, queries results, and saves waveforms/screenshots.

```json
{
  "steps": [
    {
      "type": "connect",
      "title": "Connect to Oscilloscope"
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "title": "Set CH1 to 3.3V/div, DC, 1MΩ",
      "params": {
        "command": "CH1:SCAle 3.3; CH1:COUPling DC; CH1:IMPedance ONEMeg"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "title": "Set CH2 to 3.3V/div, DC, 1MΩ",
      "params": {
        "command": "CH2:SCAle 3.3; CH2:COUPling DC; CH2:IMPedance ONEMeg"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "title": "Set up I2C Decode on Bus1: Clock=CH1, Data=CH2, Thresholds=1.65V",
      "params": {
        "command": "BUS1:TYPE IIC; BUS1:IIC:CLK CH1; BUS1:IIC:DATA CH2; BUS1:IIC:CLKTHR 1.65; BUS1:IIC:DATATHR 1.65"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "title": "Add Setup Time Measurement (CH1 falling to CH2 falling)",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUrement:ADDMEASUREMENT SETup; MEASUrement:MEAS1:SOUrce1 CH1; MEASUrement:MEAS1:EDGE1 FALL; MEASUrement:MEAS1:SOUrce2 CH2; MEASUrement:MEAS1:EDGE2 FALL"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "title": "Add Hold Time Measurement (CH2 falling to CH1 rising)",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUrement:ADDMEASUREMENT HOLD; MEASUrement:MEAS2:SOUrce1 CH2; MEASUrement:MEAS2:EDGE1 FALL; MEASUrement:MEAS2:SOUrce2 CH1; MEASUrement:MEAS2:EDGE2 RISE"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "title": "Set Trigger on I2C Address 0x48, Write Direction",
      "params": {
        "command": "TRIGger:A:TYPe BUS; TRIGger:A:BUS BUS1; TRIGger:A:BUS:BUS1:TYPE IIC; TRIGger:A:BUS:BUS1:IIC:ADDRess 0x48; TRIGger:A:BUS:BUS1:IIC:RW WRIte"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "title": "Set Single Acquisition Mode",
      "params": {
        "command": "ACQuire:STOPAfter SEQuence"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "title": "Start Acquisition",
      "params": {
        "command": "ACQuire:STATE RUN"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "error_check",
      "title": "Check for Errors"
    },
    {
      "type": "query",
      "title": "Query Setup Time Result",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUrement:MEAS1:RESUlts:CURRent:VALue?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "query",
      "title": "Query Hold Time Result",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUrement:MEAS2:RESUlts:CURRent:VALue?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "save_waveform",
      "title": "Save CH1 Waveform (Binary)",
      "params": {
        "channel": "CH1",
        "format": "BIN",
        "filename": "CH1_waveform.bin"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "save_waveform",
      "title": "Save CH2 Waveform (Binary)",
      "params": {
        "channel": "CH2",
        "format": "BIN",
        "filename": "CH2_waveform.bin"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "save_screenshot",
      "title": "Save Screenshot",
      "params": {
        "filename": "screenshot.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "disconnect",
      "title": "Disconnect from Oscilloscope"
    }
  ]
}
```

Let me know if you need any adjustments or want to add comments or delays!

